{"tid":733032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大為超重港人免費驗癌","createTime":"2018-07-07T12:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T05:55:28.000Z","uid":4880,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"297afd4a5a4d1a964c87e6a9fea6fab6cf61f0c7","tid":733032,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:08:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180706/20441648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180706%2F20441648&d=WDp8gKrEpb2cwY35X3V8FTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=48ce1986\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180706%2F20441648&h=f04007cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180706/20441648</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中大醫學院團隊8月起開展為期5年的「中大賽馬會齊心防癌計劃」。計劃獲賽馬會慈善信託基金3,500萬元捐贈，以資助團隊為1萬名年齡介乎40至75歲、以及超重即BMI（身高體重指標）超過25的港人，提供免費大腸癌、乳癌及前列腺癌篩查服務。團隊期望計劃能提供數據，以研究肥胖與癌症之間的關係，並為團隊及政府制訂更合適的癌症普查方法。<br />\n包括大腸癌乳癌等篩查<br />\n統籌計劃的中大醫學院莫慶堯醫學講座教授沈祖堯（圖）表示，社會較少關注肥胖與癌症之間的關係，但多份醫學文獻顯示肥胖是增加患癌風險因素之一。有數據指出，當人體BMI增加5單位時，其患上大腸癌的風險會增18%。他續指團隊選擇提供大腸癌、乳癌及前列腺癌的篩查服務，不但三者位列2015年全港十大常見癌症中的首、3及4位，檢查方法也較其他癌症更為低風險和容易。<br />\n<br />\n沈補充，近年腸癌患者有年輕化趨勢，女性患乳癌的高危期亦由40歲開始，故計劃涵蓋的年齡層會比政府早前的大腸癌篩查先導計劃更廣。他強調若參加者的檢查結果異常，團隊亦會為參加者安排醫療跟進或提供轉介，團隊也會為有意收身的參加者提供如太極班、營養師飲食建議等協助，令參加者學會管理體重。有意參加且合資格的市民，即日起可在網上報名（<a href=\"http://mcp.cuhk.edu.hk/form）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmcp.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fform%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=WDp8gKrEpb2cwY35X3V8FTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=871082b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mcp.cuhk.edu.hk/form）。</a><br />\n<br />\n■記者羅智堅"},{"pid":"f510222a8487a9a5affcf998cc23b518ec41c3fd","tid":733032,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:14:25.000Z","msg":"邊有咁好死"},{"pid":"4a9edcb45a3e159a5dc6602ade8591cb8e346330","tid":733032,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f510222a8487a9a5affcf998cc23b518ec41c3fd","tid":733032,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:14:25.000Z","msg":"邊有咁好死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:15:27.000Z","msg":"應該同時做埋research 呱"},{"pid":"8537a6589522e2945d5de9c7ee2245d99a284ca0","tid":733032,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f510222a8487a9a5affcf998cc23b518ec41c3fd","tid":733032,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:14:25.000Z","msg":"邊有咁好死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:15:43.000Z","msg":"團隊期望計劃能提供數據，以研究肥胖與癌症之間的關係，並為團隊及政府制訂更合適的癌症普查方法。"},{"pid":"7b8c50266cec6d381b8189c3251c539786c8bdf4","tid":733032,"uid":179938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:21:13.000Z","msg":"免費幫罪犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57715b8df3d5701adcfdd99f9aaab9f56994104","tid":733032,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:27:51.000Z","msg":"抽籤準備"},{"pid":"bc3c93b9fedce0e2fd03e930f6226ec29328bd5a","tid":733032,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:28:56.000Z","msg":"40歲up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f835a9e2e5df23d171539707ec2935f9fc2d8122","tid":733032,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:29:58.000Z","msg":"點解肥婆咁乞人憎都有得驗"},{"pid":"333350d594acded4e8958f798f6e2bba6d4e40a7","tid":733032,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:50:18.000Z","msg":"算唔算歧視？"},{"pid":"6a8d9b5df3f9531101b68f4d0f1f757f23e388c1","tid":733032,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"333350d594acded4e8958f798f6e2bba6d4e40a7","tid":733032,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:50:18.000Z","msg":"算唔算歧視？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:54:41.000Z","msg":"報